  "description": "Fix Typography Issues on Payment Information Page\n\nCorrect typography problems on the /o-przedszkolu/platnosci/ (About Preschool - Payments) page to ensure proper text rendering and readability.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify and document all typography issues on the page (incorrect fonts, sizes, spacing, alignment, special character rendering)\n- Ensure Polish language characters (ą, ć, ę, ł, ń, ó, ś, ź, ż) render correctly\n- Verify font family consistency with the rest of the site\n- Fix any line height, letter spacing, or word spacing problems\n- Correct text alignment and hierarchy issues (headings vs body text)\n- Ensure responsive typography scales properly on mobile and tablet devices\n- Validate text color contrast meets accessibility standards (WCAG AA minimum)\n- Test rendering across major browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)",
